response.overview: Attila came to Australia to have a better life. His brother was supposed to come with him, but things didn't work out as they planned. Now, he has no choice but to work for the Hungarian Mafia, but he has a plan to get away from this life. During his mission, he accidentally meets Nicole. Everything gets worse when he realised that her bother is a cop. The chase begins.
response.tagline: How far would you go to save someone you love?
response.title: Most Wanted
